<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css"> <!-- Link to your CSS file -->
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        header {
            background: #35424a;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .about-section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .about-section img {
            width: 300px;
            height: auto;
            margin-right: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .about-section div {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            background-color: #35424a;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            background: #35424a;
            color: #ffffff;
            position: relative;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Store</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="about-section">
            <img src="team.jpg" alt="Our Team">
            <div>
                <h2>Who We Are</h2>
                <p>We are a dedicated team of professionals committed to delivering the best services to our clients.
                    Our expertise spans various fields, ensuring that we can meet diverse needs effectively.</p>
                <a href="#learn-more" class="button">Learn More</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-section">
            <img src="mission.jpg" alt="Our Mission">
            <div>
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>Our mission is to innovate and provide top-notch solutions that empower our clients to achieve their
                    goals. We believe in the power of collaboration and strive to build lasting relationships.</p>
                <a href="#contact" class="button">Contact Us</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-section">
            <img src="values.jpg" alt="Our Values">
            <div>
                <h2>Our Values</h2>
                <p>Integrity, excellence, and customer satisfaction are at the core of our values. We are committed to
                    maintaining the highest standards in all our endeavors.</p>
                <a href="#values" class="button">Our Values</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <a href='/logout'>Logout</a>

    <hr>
    <hr>
